Package airportApp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Airport
    The class allows the creation of Airport objects with an id, identification (ident), name and country reference code (iso_country).
    Country
    The class allows the creation of Country objects with an id, code, name and one additional HashMap to keep track of surfaces based on task requirement 2.2.
    LunatechTask
    This is the main class that provides a command line interface for the task.
    Query
    This class is used for making queries.
    Reports
    This class is used for calling reports.
    Runway
    The class allows the creation of Runway objects with an id, airport reference (airport_ref), airport identification (airport_ident), surface, and location identification (le_ident).
    Suggestion
    The class is used to create a Suggestion object consisting of the closest word to the user input and a country code associated with it.
    Utils
    This class is used for reading an object from a csv line and possibly other utilities.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    PositiveIntegerRequiredException
    A custom made exception class for requiring positive integers.
